{"tid":2186411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建制派落選區議員吳龍飛博士 涉呃抗疫基金88萬被捕","createTime":"2020-09-03T02:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T14:25:25.000Z","uid":54373,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"df76f820172d58e74e03c93189407a36ed7f09b7","tid":2186411,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5195962/org/bad48820c08d35d4e4e0600f87966220.jpg/Vhm270u3_I3InBgLYTHVzTLiJaNBqDUrQt_2iULf9ok?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5195962%2Forg%2Fbad48820c08d35d4e4e0600f87966220.jpg%2FVhm270u3_I3InBgLYTHVzTLiJaNBqDUrQt_2iULf9ok%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=016838f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以11工廈及商住單位申資助 地點實為劏房<br />\n<br />\n其中一名被捕姓吳40歲、報稱任職物業租務及投資生意的男子，於資助計劃公佈後，以11間工廈及商住單位的地址申請資助，訛稱進行零售生意，並在門外拍攝印有業務名稱的易拉架，商業罪案調查科督察劉嘉明指，警方相信有關地點實為劏房分租生意之用，11宗申請涉及88萬元。<br />\n<br />\n過去以劏房及投資物業獲利<br />\n<br />\n吳龍飛過去經常接受傳媒訪問，指自己出身於破碎及貧困的家庭，自小讀書成績不佳，其後投身銀行業，並於2007年起購入物業，其後於物業市場投資獲利，並將持有單位「劏」成劏房出租，被稱為「80後樓神」及「劏房天王」。"},{"pid":"b10257a67e6633d9b232e35bb1fe6639bacac039","tid":2186411,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/jB1AC9NUUspMxn0KrJtl14ImFWwk0jzbn7GNO8lvy5tguvN8sqbkGleVGQN8K5jzQSvt96N6C4ggkbIbYuAY6UaQdwizYU5fgaV7zh2GrpKAUI87\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FjB1AC9NUUspMxn0KrJtl14ImFWwk0jzbn7GNO8lvy5tguvN8sqbkGleVGQN8K5jzQSvt96N6C4ggkbIbYuAY6UaQdwizYU5fgaV7zh2GrpKAUI87&h=b0cc60f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49548b779185088779f0a1f6d04f96ea126e9417","tid":2186411,"uid":108201,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:59:57.000Z","msg":"樓神？80萬都要呃，垃圾藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd29ba873d45a145cdf63925d76bfb80d5f6321","tid":2186411,"uid":58630,"like":3,"di